<eesti>Politseikadett </eesti>
<inglise>Police cadet </inglise>
<eesti>Politsei&otilde;ppeasutuse &otilde;pilane ja Sisekaitseakadeemia politseieriala &uuml;li&otilde;pilane on politseikadetid. </eesti>
<inglise>Students of police training institutions and students of the police training programme of the Estonian Public Service Academy are police cadets. </inglise>
<eesti>(11.10.2001 j&otilde;ust.08.11.2001 - RT I 2001, 85, 511) </eesti>
